<h3 id="ancestral"><strong>Ancestral</strong></h3>

<p>Recognizes territories and cultures have been handed down from generation to generation.  One example is language, which has strong connections to ancestry.  The xÊ·mÉ™Î¸kÊ·É™yÌ“É™m and É™lÌ“ilwÉ™taÉÉ¬ speak dialects of <a href="https://native-land.ca/maps/languages/hulquminum-halqemeylem-h%c9%99n%cc%93q%cc%93%c9%99min%cc%93%c9%99m%cc%93/">Hulâ€™qâ€™umiâ€™numâ€™ / Halqâ€™emÃ©ylem / hÉ™nÌ“qÌ“É™minÌ“É™mÌ“</a> and the SkwxwÃº7mesh-ulh speak <a href="https://native-land.ca/maps/languages/s%e1%b8%b5wx%cc%b1wu7mesh-snichim/">Sá¸µwxÌ±wÃº7mesh snÃ­chim</a>.</p>

